Epidemiology of knee osteoarthritis using Kellgren and Lawrence scale in Indian 
population.

Kumar H(1), Pal CP(2), Sharma YK(2), Kumar S(3), Uppal A(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedics, UP University of Medical Science, Saifai Etawah, 
